text_block.description: FF 91 is our first production vehicle and flagship model. All-electric, autonomous-ready and seamlessly connected, it embodies our latest mobility advancements in performance, intelligence, and user experience. This is the reason why we gave FF 91 a future-forward design that visually sets it apart from anything else on the road.
text_block.title: A Beautiful Future

intro.title: A Cleaner, More Electrifying Future
intro.introText: Committed to breathtaking power that also allows us to breathe more freely, our engineers are pushing the limits of electric performance and range. Designed to be highly modular, our Variable Platform Architecture (VPA) securely houses the battery, powertrain and the FF Echelon Inverter™, our first patent.

additionalScreens.title: 381 Miles per Charge
additionalScreens.description: Our lithium-ion battery cells achieve the world’s highest energy density – nearly double that of a production automotive battery. This not only represents a significant step forward in battery technology, it’s a tremendous increase in range, well in excess of 300 miles on a single charge.

props.text: FF believes the future of charging is fast, open and effortless.

videos.title: TESTING THE FF 91: DYNAMIC VEHICLE CONTROL

text_block.title: An Intelligent Future
text_block.description: Everything about our cutting-edge technology was created to make your life more connected, more engaging, more effortless. We designed our A.I. and user interaction to be as intuitive and convenient as possible, giving you back more of your invaluable time.

props.description: Your unique FFID profile encompasses an extensive range of your driving preferences and content choices. It’s how FF 91 recognizes and greets you before you enter the vehicle, and it becomes more intuitive about your preferences every time you drive. Because the more you use FF 91, the smarter about you it becomes, delivering a truly bespoke experience.
props.title: More personal with each drive

text_block.description: The next generation of automotive interiors will be redefined by dramatic innovations in mobility. Envisioning the possibilities, we designed FF 91 from the ground up as a present-day realization of tomorrow’s premium vehicle. Experience an array of well-appointed features that epitomize both modern and future luxury.
text_block.title: An Effortless Future

content.title: Defy Gravity
content.description: In zero gravity, the human body naturally assumes what NASA scientists call the Neutral Body Posture. Our rear seats are designed to these specifications and enable the ideal distribution of your body’s weight. For even more comfort, the ventilated seats can massage away pressure and stress.

props.description: Help us shape the imminent future of electric mobility. Become one of the very first to preorder the autonomous-ready, dynamically advanced FF 91. For questions, contact us at product@faradayfuture.com.
props.title: Your Future
